This website allows you (as a teacher) to keep track of your students names and grades in an easy to manage spreadsheet. With abilities to sort by name, grade and averages. Students with grade below passing, will automatically be highlighted. This project was created to meet the requirements of a job interview. 


Prerequisites
	A *nix type system or Cygwin (for Windows)
	NPM (node package manager) installed
	Tested on Google Chrome, Firefox, Microsoft Edge

To install and run 

	git clone https://github.com/dustinbrink/student_test_scores.git

	cd student_test_scores/

	npm install && npm run watch

visit in a webbrowser 
	http://localhost:8080/

for tests visit
	http://localhost:8080/test/

for Browser-Sync interface visit
	http://localhost:3001/
